com.googlecode.objectify.impl.ref

Class FirstRef<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.objectify.Ref<T>
      • com.googlecode.objectify.impl.ref.ProxyRef<T>
        • com.googlecode.objectify.impl.ref.FirstRef<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Ref<T>>

    public class FirstRef<T>
extends ProxyRef<T>

    A proxy for the first ref in an Iterator. Allows the iterator to be an async proxy, so the query can execute until our first call. If there is no first item in the iterator, proxies to a StdRef(null, null).

    Jeff Schnitzer
